Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.46,0:23:25.09,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H4B9445&}あこがれも傷も全て　今
Dialogue: 2,0:23:25.09,0:23:31.61,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\3c&H4B9445&}溶け込んで　光る
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.43,0:22:22.07,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&\fad(200,0)}水面的波纹上　那躲开的脸庞
Dialogue: 3,0:22:22.07,0:22:28.37,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}是我的心　想把荡漾藏起来
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.37,0:22:34.36,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}只要与你站在一起　我的心脏
Dialogue: 3,0:22:34.36,0:22:38.57,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&\fad(0,500)}就炽热地跳个不停
Dialogue: 3,0:22:38.57,0:22:41.67,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&\fad(300,0)}醉颜　吐息　羞赧的你
Dialogue: 3,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.51,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}今晚做个好梦
Dialogue: 3,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.52,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}两袖相接　心潮涨落
Dialogue: 3,0:22:47.52,0:22:50.41,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}我看见你眼中的我
Dialogue: 3,0:22:50.41,0:22:53.28,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}就像要将深处的光芒
Dialogue: 3,0:22:53.28,0:22:56.90,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}浅尝一口那般
Dialogue: 3,0:22:56.90,0:23:02.95,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}呼唤你的名字
Dialogue: 3,0:23:04.72,0:23:10.45,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&\fad(200,0)}滑过喉咙留下的气味
